---
title: Chorizo Hash with Parsley Aioli
description: Juicy chorizo takes centre stage with parsley aioli as its co-star in this delicious hash. What's the best part about hash? Every bite is an explosion of texture and flavour!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poelee-de-chorizo-45e7b800.jpg
